Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:01.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Everybody run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's coming. It's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We're being attacked by Bad CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:12.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In the past anime and CG have not had the best public relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.12,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The general reaction from someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:17.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,when they hear the mere mention of CG being integrated into their favorite anime
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is that they pack up and start running a fucking mile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,like they've just found out we're getting invaded by Nazis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:25.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Or even more horrifyingly,  CG Nazis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:27.43,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But today I wanted to evaluate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:30.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,if CG really deserves its reputation within the anime community.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What are some examples of it being used well and badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and what are some of the different ways that CG have been integrated into anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:41.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So first we need to answer the question what is Bad CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And here's the catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:46.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You aren't allowed to use any word that rhymes with Sheshmerk 2017.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:49.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Well if we look at the dictionary definition of Bad CG,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,we can quite clearly see that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,all for fuck's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:53.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can all agree that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,a CGI face that is noticeable enough to take you out of your immersion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and break your suspension of disbelief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:01.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and out of place objects, some stupid looking expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,A lot of things can take you out of an exprience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:05.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But that's the thing to keep in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:07.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Bad CG is Bad CG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:10.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,because you notice Bad CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:13.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Bad CG. Sorry I just wanted to say Bad CG one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:15.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I think a good place to start
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is just seeing how the general use and look of CG has evolved over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:21.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We normally associate CG with more modern age anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The have been around for a lot longer than people think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:28.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and over time has gotten better blending in objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,If you look at most mordern anime carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,you'd be hard-pressed to find one that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,doesn't incorporate some sort of computer rendered object in it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:38.11,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and a lot of the time you don't notice because it's not something that significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.37,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,There's been a lot of debate over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,how CG has changed a lot of the general look of mechs over the years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:46.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and honestly I think it comes down to how bland and forgettable modern mechs feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,They all move the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:49.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,They all feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,With the same clunky video game style that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,never looks quite as natural as hand-drawn mechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Nothing becomes as memorable
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,even if you have a cool design.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:57.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I mean fuck,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.45,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chamber{\i0} from {\i1}Suisei no Gargantia{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,had the size of seasoned Las Vegas poor dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and this was never appreciating to them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Damn……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,That is a dickass ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Whether it be to speed up the production time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or make up for a lack of talents who can animate mechs well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:19.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,it feels like CG makes a use as a compensation tool rather than a deliberate creative decision
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:23.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,because when done correctly, they look just as fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The sequences of the {\i1}Unicorn{\i0} transforming look fucking amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and the reason they do this is because they're done in CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Trying to animate this level of complicated mechanical panel movement
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,would be absurdly difficult by hand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:38.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and they managed to make it not look like an in-engine video game cut scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:41.45,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,However one thing that the industry is still figuring out how to do correctly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is with characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't matter if they are in the foreground or the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,There's an old Chinese proverb that goes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,unless that crosswalk contains a CG anime crowd
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.37,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,in which case you're probably burning in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:02.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Yeah CGI crowds are the one thing I think are destined to always look like complete shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:04.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Nothing's more distracting than when there's something important going on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but your brain unable to focus on anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but the same 5 PlayStation 2 motherfuckers hangout in the background
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,trying have horrendously bad to blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why does your face look like Bad CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why does everyone look like Bad CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,My mind is Bad CG nightmare right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And I really did try finding a good example of anime CGI crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So if anyone does have any good examples
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,then please contact me at
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But this extends the foreground characters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where you have to battle against this weird {\i1}Uncanny Valley{\i0} effect
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where characters kind of like anime but not anime enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,So when they're just there front and center with no attempt to blend it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:48.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Your brain has time to process what you're watching so you kind of notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:48.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,These are the same guys they hired to do the {\i1}Mass Effect: Andromeda{\i0} facial animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Even when they look competent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,When you are restricted to 3D models emulating a 2D-R-style,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.05,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,there is less freedom to work with when it comes to subtle expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Nuanced character animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.54,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And even the best examples we've had so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:14.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,don't even come close to the best examples in 2D animation yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Things are looking better
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but the next problem is actually being able to blend these two elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:22.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The issue you face when you blend 2D animation with 3D elements
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is the aesthetic clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,When we are watching an animated show,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,we know it is an animated show that does not exist within our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But we are fully invested in suspending our disbelief for that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\fs37}However, if you see two objects that blatantly look like they don't belong in the same universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.91,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,it was against that suspension of disbelief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Golden Kamuy{\i0} is the latest example of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where you have a standard anime characters fighting that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:49.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,fucking bear from {\i1}Far Cry 5{\i0} with a cel-shaded wolf in a background of green screen fire effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The visual cohesion is an absolute mess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}and personally I much prefer this early leaked test footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:59.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}At least it has a uniform visual style which you know just makes the fights
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's just far more believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Oh no, an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Different aesthetics only really work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,when the {\u1}juxtaposition{\u0} is purposefully part of the visual style
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or when it's supposed to happen narratively.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,There are, however, effective ways to blend the two elements that we are seeing more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,When CG is limited to dynamic background environments,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,the fast-paced movement of the foreground animation is only enhanced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,allowing for more freedom of camera movements
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,which results in being able to complex shot like this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,without giving the viewer adequate time to notice the aesthetic clash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:36.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,There are countless examples from {\i1}Attack on Titan{\i0} to {\i1}Code Geass: Akito the Exiled,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,even some of the more intricate shot from {\i1}Monogatari{\i0} which fully take advantage of this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:44.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or with other shows that had some shots that were rotoscoped with the aid of CG tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The important thing is that the CG is never the main focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:51.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Always rendered in such a way that it naturally fits in with the visual style of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,In this sense, {\i1}Ufotable{\i0} are the fucking gods at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Throughout the years they have perfected the art of the digital composition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and blending traditional animation with computer-aided effects
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,to the point where you can hardly tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:05.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,My first exposure to them was their first take on the {\i1}Fate{\i0} franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And then no no not you get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:11.97,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Another time they blew me away and I thought anime couldn't look better than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.45,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But then they came back with {\i1}Unlimited Blade Works{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,No, not, fucking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,They have continually improved and you and pushed the boundaries so much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:22.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,so that they have crafted a unique visual style which is instantly recognizable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and no one really calls this CG anime
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.45,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,despite how much they use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.88,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But moving on a different problem from blending 2D and 3D
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.57,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,when you are completely switching between the two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.71,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Let me set the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You're enjoying a classic show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It looks awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The characters look great and we're just about to get to the heart pumping action scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Then without any warning it cuts to the action
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:45.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and you noticed something's a bit off about way the show looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And then just as you get used to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,it switches back before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.91,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And you like, "Okay, maybe my eyes are being funny".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:54.25,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Then you begin to look really closely and slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:59.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You realize that maybe there is something different about the way the show looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Constantly switching from 2D to 3D to 2D again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is a guaranteed method to make the viewer feel a sense of visual whiplash.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And this {\u1}semi{\u0} is right up there with CG crowds for anime things
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that fucking keep me up at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.94,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The most recent offenders I can think of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.64,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,are with {\i1}Inuyashiki{\i0} and the {\i1}Berserk{\i0} movie trilogy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:20.04,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and the thing is the CG sometimes doesn't even look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't even mind if some of these shows were fully 3D.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's just a note don't shut shut the fuck up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.30,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Just the constant switching between visual styles
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.46,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that break any kind of immerging you could be having.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:33.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And I would prefer it so much if they just chose one style and committed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I mean we've all heard of {\i1}Jazz hands{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But have you tried the hottest trend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Bad CG piano man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What people don't normally talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.59,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,however is that the switch can be done well
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.84,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,if we stick to some of the same rules we talked about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.30,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}KILL la KILL{\i0} was a good example.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.66,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,If I tell you {\i1}KILL la KILL{\i0} used a lot CG
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,your mind will probably go back to that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.77,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,one time Satsuki was apparently ice-skating vertically up a building which
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,How can I adequately put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But what you probably don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is just how many cuts were completely CG like this shot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:04.58,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or this shot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.26,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or this entire sequence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.12,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,where they built an entirely new 3D model
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.48,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,just to accentuates these few frames
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:14.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and unless you were flicking through frame by frame and know exactly what to look for
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.46,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,you won't even notice exactly because it was the sky so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,As opposed to being loaded front and center.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But that leads into the Big Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.72,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,If there was a final boss for the anime industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.00,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,this would be it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and for most of the time so far
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,anime has handled it about as well as
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:34.37,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,a Facebook surfing candy crush addicted grandma attempting no hits run on Dark Souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.70,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The problem with a lot of us had with early CG anime
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,was that they seemingly came in with the approach of trying to emulate the 2D art style
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.70,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,with a completely different tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And it doesn't take a genius to tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,if you aren't using your tools correctly it probably won't go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Movement felt restricted and robotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.38,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Characters just weren't as expressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The frame rate sometimes looks really dodgy as they purposely restricted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Something even one guy who helped make silly Internet videos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,figured out was a dumb fuck idea before an entire industry did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.04,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,They didn't play to their strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But despite this, as time went on, things began improving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.10,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Acceptable shows started appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,We slowly started to accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Maybe there could be a space for CG anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.92,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And just as we thought things were starting to look up,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.54,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Berserk (2016){\i0} came crashed landing into the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the collective effort of every half piece of CG anime come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,we managed to stop this from ruining everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Quick, {\i1}Polygon Pictures{\i0} release something half decent and maybe we can get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.31,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kemono Friends{\i0}, {\i1}Nobunaga Concerto{\i0}, {\i1}Kado{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.58,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,These were fully 3D shows that managed to be enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:42.80,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But the problem is I feel these shows were enjoyable in spite of CGs not because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Over the years {\i1}Polygon Pictures{\i0} have tried their damned hardest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.50,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,to make a case for fully 3D anime
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.10,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and continually improves with every project they work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But to me it's the same problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.96,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that makes me think
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.24,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I would rather see these shows using CG over traditional animation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.78,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,if given a expected choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:01.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,That is until we got the one show we were waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.72,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Land of the Lustrous{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.84,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,A show like this was a long time coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.84,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But despite how many opinions it changed about CG anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.66,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,it didn't really do anything new that we have already discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.38,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,What it did do was understand what the strengths were for CG as a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.66,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and play to those strengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,The CG crystal effects of metallic textures
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,gave the show a unique visual identity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.34,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,that wouldn't be a striking if in 2D.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:26.26,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And the number of dynamic shots it was able to pull off in his action scenes chases
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or just using long shots to build this claustrophobic tension
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:32.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,is something that could only achieved using CG.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Hopefully by the end of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.14,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,you can get the idea that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.04,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,despite the reputation CG in anime has right now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:40.20,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,CG can look good and has looked good for years
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.28,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,even if you're not a fan of the aesthetics scene in {\i1}Polygon Pictures'{\i0} works
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.38,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,or {\i1}Land of the Lustrous{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,you've probably appreciated it even if you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But that's just it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.82,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,It's a lose-lose situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because if CG does its job well,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,it won't even be noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.74,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but if it does fail
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:59.40,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,then it's forever doomed to have some shitty anime youtuber cement it into meme history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.98,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Its failures are exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.30,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and its successes are ignored
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.52,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,but it's important to note that whether it's good or bad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.02,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,largely depends on the understanding from the creater
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.46,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,of the strengths and limitations of working with CG as a tool
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.70,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,as it is with every other medium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.51,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,CG has become a standard part of anime nowadays
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.65,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,so if you're not a fan of that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.22,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,then I can suggest that you watch order anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.64,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Take the 80s for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.68,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Computer effects may have started to become revolutionary in Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.86,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,But anime was still untouched and pure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:26.97,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,You know back then
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:32.17,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,they would never ruin their anime by rendering things using ugly PlayStation 1 graphics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:37.64,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Because they were too busy rendering things with a fucking Atari 2600.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.56,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why is your helicopter Bad CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.10,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why is your face Bad CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.86,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Why is your life Bad CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.16,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, hope you enjoyed the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.96,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much this month too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.85,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and everyone else on my patreon for helping to support me for this month
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.62,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,and making this video possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:18.04,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,As you can see I've changed my location back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.60,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I am back in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.32,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,And I will be attending AX in LA in just a few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.08,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,I have a very busy schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.42,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}so if you're going to be attending AX as well
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.04,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}keep an eye out for that as I'll be posting that soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.54,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Anyway that's it for me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.70,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Not too many updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:38.44,720P思源英文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}But until then I've been giguk and I will see you all next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:01.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们被差CG攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:12.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在过去 动画和CG的关系并没有现在这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.12,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,对某人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:17.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当他们听说自己最爱的动漫中有CG的制作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们肯定会对此非常嫌弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就像被辣脆入侵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:25.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者更恐怖的东西 CG辣脆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:27.43,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是今天我想评估一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.43,0:00:30.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,CG技术是否在动漫社群中获得了应有的名声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,哪些是CG技术运用的优秀例子或者失败例子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:36.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,还有就是动漫中的CG技术又是以哪些方式被运用的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.85,0:00:41.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,首先我们需要定义差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:42.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,举个例
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:46.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你不可以用任何和Sheshmerk 2017押韵的词汇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:49.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果我们仔细阅读差CG的词典定义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:51.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们就很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,都是些辣鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:53.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有一点可以达成共识
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那就是一张CGI的脸足够让你失去看番的沉浸感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,中止你对这个世界的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:01.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,包括一些不能突兀的物体 一些崩坏的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,许多东西都会影响你的观看体验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:05.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有一件事你需要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:07.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,差CG就是差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:10.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为你注意到了差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.31,0:01:13.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,差CG 对不起我只是想再说一遍差CG这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:15.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如何展开这个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,首先是要看看CG技术是如何逐渐地被广泛地应用与观看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:21.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,一般而言 我们更多地把CG技术与现代动画联系起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过CG技术的出现远比人们想象中的早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:28.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而且逐渐更加擅长用于物体的渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果你仔细地观看各种现代动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你很难找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.22,0:01:34.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那些不使用CG技术渲染物体的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:38.11,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,更多的情况下你甚至都注意不到这个问题 因为这无关紧要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:39.37,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,人们总在争论
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:42.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,CG技术这些年来是如何大幅改变机甲动画的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:46.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,实话说这就涉及到了现代机甲动画是有多么平淡乏味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:47.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们动作一致
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.60,0:01:49.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,观感一致
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,都像是笨重的电子游戏风格
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,永远也没有手绘机甲那样地自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,再也没有以前那样令人难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,即使你的机设很帅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:57.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我是指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:01:59.45,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}翠星的伽鲁冈缇亚{\i0} 的机甲{\i1}Chamber{\i0} 的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就和拉斯维加斯经验丰富的舞者的房间一样大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而这么说还是夸奖了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:06.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,可恶……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,贼鸡儿恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:11.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不管是为了加速生产时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者是为了弥补无法设计出好机甲的不足才能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:19.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就像是CG技术是用来随意填补漏洞的手段而非故意使用的创意工具
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:23.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为CG技术运用得当的话并不会比传统机甲动画差到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:26.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,高达UC那段变形看着着实过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:29.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而正因为使用了CG技术才能做到如此优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:32.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,想要制做这样复杂的机械运动动画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:34.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,几乎不可能用纯手绘的方法办到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:38.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而他们设法做到了让这一切看起来不像是电子游戏的剧情动画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:41.45,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,然而 有一件事业界还在探索当中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那就是人物的CG渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不管是前景人物还是背景人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有个中国古代谚语说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是不适用于充满了CG渲染人群的路口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.37,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这种情况下你可能会被烧死在地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:02.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,没错 我始终认为CG渲染的人群不论在任何情况下都像一坨屎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:04.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当剧情进展到关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,没什么比这更让人分心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:09.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就是你大脑只能关注着背景里5个PS2画质的路人而无法关注在剧情上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,糟糕得完全不能融入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为什么你的脸看上去像差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:18.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为什么每个人都像差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我的大脑现在也充满着差CG噩梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我确实尝试找过CG渲染人群的优秀例子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:27.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,所以如果有人能找到CG渲染人群的优秀例子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,请按照以下邮箱联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是对于前景角色而言也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你需要对抗奇怪的{\i1}恐怖谷{\i0} 理论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:41.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,角色看起来像动画但还不够动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当他们处在中间或者前面的位置但完全无法融入环境的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:48.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你的大脑需要时间处理 某种程度上你会注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:48.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些人应该也做{\i1}质量效应: 仙女座{\i0} 的表情动画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,即使看起来能胜任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当你被限制用3D模型模仿2D渲染风格的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.05,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,处理那些细微的表情变化就变得更加困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,角色的细节动画
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:09.54,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,即使是我们现在能举出的最佳例子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:14.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,和2D动画中的最好的例子比起来 也难以望其项背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:15.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过事情正在向好的方向发展
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:19.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过下一个问题是如何从实际角度出发让这两种元素融合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:22.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在2D动画中融入3D元素
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你面临的问题是美学意义上的冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们看动画的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们知道这是现实中不存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是我们又投入大量精力去相信那个世界的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:36.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是 如果你看到两个物体显然不属于同一个世界的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:38.91,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就会抵触你对这个世界的信任感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}黄金神威{\i0} 是这方面最新的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在这个动画里面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:49.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,2D的角色和{\i1}孤岛惊魂5{\i0} 里卡通渲染版本的狼在绿幕火焰效果的背景中作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,视觉效果一团糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就我个人而言 我更喜欢这段早期泄漏版本的测试短片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:59.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,至少它有个统一的视觉风格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,让这场战斗更可信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:03.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,看 那有天使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不同的美学元素混搭仅在以下几种情况起正面作用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:09.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这种混搭本身就是视觉风格的重要组成部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者是作用于叙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然也有更常见的 更加有效的方法让这两者融合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当CG技术的运用仅限于动态背景的环境当中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这增强了前景动画的高速运动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.48,0:05:23.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,允许摄像机更自由地移动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这将允许更复杂的镜头譬如这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:32.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而不给观众足够的时间发觉这种冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:36.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在动画{\i1}自由之翼{\i0} 或者{\i1}Code Geass 亡国的阿基德{\i0} 中 这样的例子太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:40.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,甚至在{\i1}物语系列{\i0} 中一些更加复杂的镜头 也是充分利用到了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.51,0:05:44.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,至于有些动画则是有些镜头借助了CG技术转描成2D部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:47.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,重要的是 CG技术永远不是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:51.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,CG技术总是按照融入动画视觉风格的方式来渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:54.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,在这方面来讲 {\i1}Ufotable{\i0} 简直高到不知道哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些年来他们完善了数字构图的作画方式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,让传统动画以电脑辅助效果的方式渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,达到了一种你无法分清二者的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:05.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我对此的第一次体验是他们参与制作的第一个{\i1}Fate{\i0} 系列
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:07.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当然不是你这个{\i1}菲特/今晚留下来(2006){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:11.97,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们又一次震撼到我了 我以为这就是动画的极致
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.45,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,之后他们又推出了{\i1}Fate/stay night [Unlimited Blade Works]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不 不是你{\i1}菲特/今晚留下来 [无限刀片工作] 剧场版(2010){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们还在持续改进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:22.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,达到了一种独特可辨识的视觉风格的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而没有人称这个动画是CG动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.45,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,尽管这个动画使用了非常多的CG技术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:29.88,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,继续探讨一个关于渲染2D和3D的不同的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.57,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,当你完全切换两者的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:33.71,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,让我来假设一种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你正在观看一个传统2D动画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:36.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,看起来好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,角色看起来都很棒 很快就要进入到精彩的动作场景了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:41.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而在没有任何预警的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:45.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画就切换到了一种你能察觉出的完全不同的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正当你习惯了这种风格的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它又切换到之前的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:50.91,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你会感觉到 {\i1}好吧 我的眼睛瞎了{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:54.25,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,接下来你会很仔细很缓慢地观看着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:59.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你会察觉到也许这个动画就是看起来有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,经常在2D和3D之间切换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,绝对会让观众感到视觉疲劳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:10.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而这正如CG渲染人群一样的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:12.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,是让我晚上睡不着觉的噩梦原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.94,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,最近的几个类似的糟糕动画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:16.64,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,是{\i1}犬屋敷{\i0} 和{\i1}剑风传奇{\i0} 电影三部曲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:20.04,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我想表达的是 有时CG本身看着没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我甚至不在意这些动画是全3D的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,只是提一下 你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.30,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过是反复切换视觉风格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.46,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就会摧毁你之前看动画的各种沉浸感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:33.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我非常希望他们只选择一种风格 并忠于一种风格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我的意思是我们都听说过{\i1}Jazz hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是你尝试过最新的潮流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.16,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,譬如差CG钢琴演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:41.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,人们经常不会讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.59,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就是这种切换其实可以做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:45.84,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果遵循以下几个规则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.30,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}斩服少女{\i0} 就是一个正面例子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:49.66,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果我说{\i1}斩服少女{\i0} 用到了很多CG技术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你可能会回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.77,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,有一次鬼龙院皐月垂直滑上一个建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,还有比这更合适的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但你可能不知道的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,类似这个镜头里 非常多的剪辑都是完全由CG技术制作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:04.58,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者这个镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.26,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,亦或是这个片段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:08.12,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们制作了完整的全新的3D模型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.48,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,仅仅是为了做这么少数几张画面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:14.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,除非你一帧一帧地仔细观看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.46,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你甚至不会察觉到 因为背景做得实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而不是放在前景或者中心的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是这就讲到了最关键的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:25.72,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画产业遇到的最大的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:27.00,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,会是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,多数情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动画处理它就如同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:34.37,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,一个平时就刷刷脸书沉迷消消乐的老奶奶尝试无伤通关黑魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.70,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们遇到的许多早期CG动画的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就是他们想要找一种尝试模仿2D艺术风格的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.70,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而使用完全不同的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,很显然的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:46.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,工欲善其事必先利其器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,动作僵化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:50.38,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,角色僵化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为刻意的限制 张数看起来很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\a6}就算是那种做傻x互联网视频的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:59.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,都在整个业界之前了解到这是个愚蠢的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.04,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们没有充分利用CG的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:04.16,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不管这件事 随着时间的流逝 事情也在变得越来越好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.10,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,令人可以接受的CG动画开始出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,作为观众的我们也逐渐开始接受这类动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:11.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,也许CG动画能存活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.92,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而正如我们觉着事情正在往好的方向发展的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:17.54,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}剑风传奇(2016){\i0} 灾难性地出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:18.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,哎我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过还好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,感谢半吊子CG动画的集体出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我们成功阻止了这部作品(而让这些作品)毁灭了CG动画的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,快点 {\i1}Polygon Pictures{\i0} 发布了某些半成品动画 也许我们能逃离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.31,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}动物朋友{\i0} {\i1}信长协奏曲{\i0} {\i1}正确的卡多{\s1}·反腐先锋{\s0}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:37.58,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些都是让人感到愉悦的全3D动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:42.80,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得这些动画让我感到愉悦的原因并非CG技术而是CG技术以外的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:45.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些年来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:47.50,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Polygon Pictures{\i0} 全力为全3D动画创造市场空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:50.10,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,并持续改进他们制作的每个项目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但对我而言 问题都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.96,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些都并不足以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.24,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,让我宁愿看CG动画而不是传统2D动画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.78,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果在可以选择的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:01.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,直到我们等到了那个我们一直以来期待的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.72,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,{\i1}宝石之国{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.84,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这样的一部动画需要很长时间的酝酿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.84,0:10:07.84,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但不管有多少关于CG动画的观点因此而改变
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.66,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,并没有改变我们之前所讨论的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:14.38,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它所做到的是让我们理解使用CG作为工具的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.66,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,并充分利用这些优势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,金属纹理带来的水晶CG效果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.16,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,给动画带来了独特的视觉特征
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.34,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果在2D情况下就不会有如此冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:26.26,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,而成功运用动态镜头拍摄出的追逐场景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者使用长镜头来渲染这种幽闭恐惧的紧张氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:32.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,都是只有使用CG技术才能达到的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,希望你在看完视频之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.14,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.04,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不论现在CG动画拥有的名誉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:40.20,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这些年来CG动画看起来都挺不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.28,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就算你不喜欢{\i1}Polygon Pictures{\i0} 那些作品的艺术风格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.38,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,或者你也不喜欢{\i1}宝石之国{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你也会感谢那些你并不知道的CG技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:48.16,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过也就仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:49.82,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,这是一个双输的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为如果CG技术运用得炉火纯青
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它甚至不会被察觉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.74,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是如果它失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:59.40,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,就会被彻底毁掉 并被某些辣鸡油管播主加入陈年老梗豪华午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.98,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,它的失败被曝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.30,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是成功却无人问津
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:04.52,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不过不管这是好是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.02,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,绝大部分都取决于
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.46,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,创作者是否理解作为工具的CG技术的优势和限制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.70,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正如许多其他媒介中对CG技术的运用一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:15.51,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,现在CG技术成为了动画制作中的一个标准环节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.65,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,所以如果你讨厌它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:19.22,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那么我建议你看点老动画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.64,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,譬如80年代的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.68,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,那时候 好莱坞正掀起了一波电脑特效革命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.86,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,但是动画领域依然保留着那份2D的纯真与美好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:26.97,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:32.17,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,他们绝不会用辣鸡PS1画质来毁灭他们的动画
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:37.64,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,因为他们正忙着用更辣鸡的雅达利2600的画质
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄dei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.56,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为什么你的直升机是差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:51.10,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为什么你的脸是差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.86,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,为什么你的绳命也是差CG
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:01.16,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,大家好 希望你们看得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.96,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,同样也感谢这个月的这些赞助者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.85,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,以及任何其他这个月在patreon上支持我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.62,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,没有你们无法做出这期视频
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:18.04,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,正如你所看到的 我又换了地理位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.60,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,我又回美国了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.32,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,几周后会参加洛杉矶漫展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.08,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,日程会有些紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.42,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,如果你也参加洛杉矶漫展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.04,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,注意我会很快提到这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.54,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,不管怎么说 今天先到这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.70,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,更新不是很多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:38.44,720P思源中文标准位置,,0,0,0,,下次再见
